      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CONTROL BUBBA (4) boasts a strong record this journey here with three wins and two minors from six tries. Scored by 1.5 lengths last time (22.40) in a Grade 5 /MDN over 383m at this track. Looks the one to beat with even luck. CHRONIC (7) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten one length, (18.47) at this track. Expected to be in this for a long way. MUM KNOWS BEST (2) comes off an average run last start when sixth at this track over 312m behind Scotch Finger (19.04) in a Grade 4/5. Scored at his previous run. Has a solid record from this box including two wins and a minor placing. Should be in this for a long way. CANYA MOLLY (8) profiles nicely over this trip.",
